videos.description: Kenny Williams steals the ball then races down court to split defenders and score his first field goal of the 2018-2019 season
videos.headline: Williams steals ball, scores for 1st bucket of season

videos.description: Stanford's Trevor Stanback goes up to slam it, but the rim negates him.
videos.headline: Leaky steals in-bound and slams it

videos.description: UNC's Leaky Black steals an inbounds pass from Stanford and runs down the court to throw it down.
videos.headline: Leaky steals inbounds pass and slams it

videos.description: Stanford's Cormac Ryan tosses up a deep 3-pointer and banks it in while falling.
videos.headline: Stanford's Ryan banks in deep 3 while falling

videos.description: Luke Maye hits a 3-pointer at the buzzer to put North Carolina up double at the half, 52-26.
videos.headline: Maye hits 3 at buzzer as UNC doubles up Stanford at halftime
